											<p>The personal information provided to or collected by our Services is controlled by Pro-Filr Inc, 10 George St. North, Brampton. ON L6X 1R2 Canada in respective of your location.</p>
											
											<p><b>If you have any concern about providing information to us or having such information displayed on our Services or otherwise used in any manner permitted in this Privacy Policy and the User Agreement, you should not become a Member, visit our websites, apps or otherwise use our Services</b>. If you have already registered, you can close your accounts. We collect your personal information in the following ways:</p></dd>
									</dl>
