											<p>We make other tools available to sync information with our Services, and may also develop additional features that allow Members to use their account in conjunction with other third-party services. For example, our mobile applications allow you to sync your device’s calendar, email and/or contacts apps with our Services to show you the Pro-Filr.com profiles of meeting attendees, email correspondents and/or your contacts.</p>
